<bibRefCitation author="Mazur, S." box="[1168,1231,1457,1483]" pageId="68" pageNumber="265" refId="ref74858" refString="Mazur, S. (2004) Histeridae. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Smetana, A. (Eds), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera, Volume 2. Hydrophiloidea - Staphylinoidea. Apollo Books, Stenstrup, pp. 68 - 102." type="book" year="2004">2004</bibRefCitation>
