<bibRefCitation author="Yelamos, T. &amp; Lackner, T." box="[188,532,1532,1558]" pageId="68" pageNumber="265" refId="ref77231" refString="Yelamos, T. &amp; Lackner, T. (2004) Fauna Europaea: Histeridae. In: Alonso-Zarazaga, M. A. (Ed.), Fauna Europaea: Coleoptera 1. Fauna Europaea version 1.1, available at http: // www. faunaeur. org [accessed September 2009 as version 1.3 of April 19 th 2007.]" type="url" year="2004">Yélamos and Lackner (2004)</bibRefCitation>
